{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "我有一個榮美家鄉", "storyInfo": "修道院中眾人各有盤算，剛到達此地的費德里科一行被這裡的居民攔在大門之外。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g9_monasteryroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那時恰好是秋天，我與幾名逃離家鄉的伊比利亞人同行，行走在荒無人煙的荒野上。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "就在我們以為我們將會困死在此處時，面前出現了那座修道院。它就好像是某種奇蹟，某種不可能存在於現實中的救贖。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "托雷格羅薩主教閣下接納了那些無處可去的人。他是一位值得尊敬的老人，是最虔誠的信教者。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在主教閣下的管理下，這座被困於荒野的修道院恍若被從世間割離，成為某種異境。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在這裡，本不可能有交集的人們和諧共處，互相依靠。儘管生活清貧，但人們不分彼此，都在為了生活而努力。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個字跡，果然是......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當我提出自己的請求時，主教閣下沉默許久後對我說，他不願拒絕任何需要幫助的人，可我提出的地方太過遙遠，他無能為力。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或許是因為本就不懷太多期望，因此，在被拒絕時我也並不失望。拒絕我的無理請求，主教閣下看起來比我更愧疚難堪。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我為得見這樣一處善人的樂園而深感欣慰，可與此同時，我也難以抑制地想到這樣的問題：", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這樣一處不適應土壤的奇蹟，是否真的能長存於這片大地之上？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......或許我在這裡停留得是有些久了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我該再度啟程，去往拉特蘭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“本不可能有交集的人們”“不分彼此”......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#2$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，在最初看到那樣的景象時，我也有些懷疑自己的眼睛。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果只是作為我個人來說的話，真希望這樣難得的和平能一直一直持續下去。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安小姐，你在忙嗎？", "name": "修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前你提過的那種正在流行的圖案，我和其他人嘗試著繡了一些在被褥上，你看這樣對嗎？", "name": "修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看看......嗯嗯，你們的手藝很好呢，這個就算擺在商店裡賣，我也不會感到奇怪的。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒你誇的這麼厲害......", "name": "修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在天氣涼了，蕾繆安小姐這裡的被褥可能不大保暖，大家就湊了點布料送過來。", "name": "修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝關心~", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過給我的話，你們那裡會不會不夠用？還是優先分給大家吧。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別看我這樣，其實我很強壯，不會輕易生病的哦。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#10$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我們沒關係的，大夥分一分多少還是沒問題的。", "name": "修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是蕾繆安小姐，看著也不像是很強壯的樣子啊，拉特蘭也真是的，怎麼派蕾繆安小姐出這麼遠的門？", "name": "修道院居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_934_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，這個嘛......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個問題，我也很想問一問我的上級呢。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g7_chapel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_936_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼我們不回去？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_936_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為萊蒙德他們不能和我們一起！這個理由還不足夠？", "name": "德爾菲娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_936_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_936_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你要拋下他們？我做不到！", "name": "德爾菲娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_936_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（笨蛋菲娜，難道我看起來是這麼冷血的人嗎？要把從小一起長大的朋友丟下，這我當然也做不到啊。）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（可是繼續像現在這樣僵持下去也不是辦法，最近大家脾氣都開始變壞了......）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（真的就沒有什麼更好的解決方法了嗎？）", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，怎麼又唉聲歎氣？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真稀奇，怎麼就你一個人，德爾菲娜竟然沒和你在一起？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#8$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這話什麼意思，我和菲娜也不是時時刻刻都在一起吧？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#9$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多吧，你們不是關係好得就差睡一張床了嗎。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#9$2"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們有時候是會一起睡......呃，不對，重點不是這個！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你什麼時候回來的？我聽說你跟著杰拉爾德叔叔出去狩獵了，這次還順利嗎？有沒有受傷？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你受傷了一定要說出來，千萬別學杰拉爾德叔叔，什麼都自己忍著。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，你別瞎操心。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我瞎操心？上回受傷不說最後傷口發炎的人是誰？私自去礦脈差點回不來的又是誰？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，好，算我錯了！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？“算你錯了”？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我錯了。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#8$2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "福爾圖娜。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我來是想問問你，你......還有德爾菲娜，當然，也包括其他人。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是想問，你們要不要和我們一起......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青年的話語在中途停住了。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他忽然沉默起來。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#2$2"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了，沒什麼。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#8$2"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一會我要出去一趟，可能得晚一點回來。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "福爾圖娜，晚餐前你能來樓頂的聖堂一趟嗎？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把德爾菲娜也喊上......我有件事要告訴你們。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$2"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g4_gatheringplace_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看看，這是什麼情況？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在修道院旁邊還建了一條街？這都建到移動地塊邊緣去了......修道院裡的空間有這麼緊張嗎？明明看起來大得很欸。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的人口有這麼多嗎？要養活一大群人不容易吧......特別還是在這樣的荒野中央。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進去看看就知道了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有人來了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？啊，從裡面走過來，應該是當地的居民吧？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫曼那傢伙，到底去哪了......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨，看不清臉的帥哥，下午好啊。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！什麼人？！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光環......你們是薩科塔。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你們是什麼人，有什麼目的，都不許再靠近了！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛見面，別這麼劍拔弩張，大家都和氣一點，哎，好好說話。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "午安，這位先生，我們三人來自拉特蘭，不是什麼可疑人物，請別緊張......如果能把你手上的武器收起來就更好了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#3$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭的人來這種荒郊野嶺有何貴幹？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$2"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我們是受教宗閣下派遣，來這裡尋找我們的兩位同僚......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是在浪費時間，里凱萊。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從表現來看，我認為他很清楚我們的身份與來此的動機，並且懷有敵意。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對拉特蘭很反感，表現出了明顯的排斥以及不滿。你的敵意從何而來？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道你在說什麼。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#10$2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直站在通向側方街道的入口處。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id"