": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有挑釁。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你們這些拉特蘭人就是這樣，突然出現，把一切都攪得一團亂......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從資料上看，這裡的狀況本就不容樂觀。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你再說一遍。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想動手嗎？來啊，我奉陪。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#5$2"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊還真是劍拔弩張......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝費德里科總能吸引所有目光，偷跑比我想的要輕鬆。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figu