, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g4_gatheringplace_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了好了，別這麼說話，費德里科。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的發言並沒有問題。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之你暫時先別說話。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#9$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這位小兄弟，別衝動，我們真的只是來找下落不明的同事，不管你，嗯，不管你是什麼人，我們都沒有敵意。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，說得好聽。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你管他這樣的叫沒有敵意？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，我可以發誓。總之......可以先放我們進去嗎？如果方便通知一下這邊的負責人就最好不過了。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯普莉雅......咦，斯普莉雅人呢？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她已經進去了。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？那個女人什麼時候——？！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘖！不能讓你們拉特蘭的人在這撒野！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們兩個，不是要見主教閣下嗎，跟我來！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......也好，這是同意我們進去的意思，對吧？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#10$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我警告你們，別想著和那個女人一樣亂跑——", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好了！快、快來人！", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒？怎麼了，發生什麼事了？！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#6$2"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德！太好了，快通知其他人——", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有敵襲？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，是的！不對，萊蒙德，這兩位是......？", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#3$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別管他們！具體是什麼情況？！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$2"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對，對......不好了！", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛修繕窗戶時，看到不遠處有些動靜——", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#11$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前的那群強盜，他們又來了！", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#6$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}